问题 6¶

Q-Learning3Q-table

  • Q-Learning
  • $\epsilon$
  • $\epsilon$
  • ?

回答：¶

Q-Learning

10$\epsilon$

$\epsilon$ exploration factor()

FC$\epsilon$tolerance

改进Q-Learning驾驶代理程序¶

Q-LearningQ-LearningQ-Learning$\epsilon = 1$Q-Learning

改进Q-Learning的模拟结果¶

Q-learning

  • 'enforce_deadline' - True
  • 'update_delay' - 0.01
  • 'log_metrics' - True/logs/.csvQ-table.txt
  • 'learning' - 'True'Q-Learning
  • 'optimized' - 'True'Q-Learning

Q-Learning

  • 'n_test' - 10
  • 'alpha' - 0 - 1Q-Learning
  • 'epsilon' - 0 - 1Q-Learning
  • 'tolerance' - 00.05epsilon

$\epsilon$ ()'tolerance'Q-Learning($t$)

$$ \epsilon = a^t, \textrm{for } 0 < a < 1 \hspace{50px}\epsilon = \frac{1}{t^2}\hspace{50px}\epsilon = e^{-at}, \textrm{for } 0 < a < 1 \hspace{50px} \epsilon = \cos(at), \textrm{for } 0 < a < 1$$

$\alpha$ $0 \leq \alpha \leq 1$ 'verbose'True
